claim.claim-text:
A rechargeable battery, comprising:
a pouch type case (25, 60, 70, 80);
an electrode assembly (10) housed within the case (25, 60, 70, 80);
electrode tabs connected to the electrode assembly, the electrode tabs protruding from a first end of the case;
wherein a second end of the case comprises a recessed portion in the second end of the case;
wherein the rechargeable battery further comprises a support member (42, 62, 72, 82) adjacent an outer surface of the second end of the case (25, 60, 70, 80), the support member (42, 62, 72, 82) arranged to maintain a shape of the second end of the case (25, 60, 70, 80).
